pull_request.title: Offline version
pull_request.body:
Opening a pull request because it's Hacktoberfest and I need to complete 4 pull requests 🙃

An offline version of the website with all server/API communication removed. 

- Website is now responsive.
- User can input their name instead of their TD ID.
- Added a submit button
- Personal details are generated based on a seed provided by the user.
- User spending data is always randomized.
